Grammar

    0 $accept: query $end

    1 query: clause_list

    2 clause_list: mod_clause
    3            | clause_list mod_clause
    4            | clause_list AND mod_clause
    5            | clause_list OR mod_clause

    6 mod_clause: term_expr
    7           | PLUS term_expr
    8           | MINUS term_expr
    9           | NOT term_expr

   10 term_expr: boosted_expr

   11 @1: ε

   12 term_expr: TERM COLON @1 term_expr

   13 boosted_expr: modified_term
   14             | modified_term CARET NUMBER
   15             | modified_term CARET FLOAT

   16 modified_term: base_term
   17              | TERM TILDE
   18              | TERM TILDE NUMBER
   19              | PHRASE TILDE
   20              | PHRASE TILDE NUMBER

   21 base_term: TERM
   22          | PHRASE
   23          | REGEX
   24          | PREFIX
   25          | SUFFIX
   26          | WILDCARD
   27          | range_expr

   28 @2: ε

   29 base_term: LPAREN @2 clause_list RPAREN

   30 range_expr: LBRACKET range_bound TO range_bound RBRACKET
   31           | LBRACE range_bound TO range_bound RBRACE
   32           | LBRACKET range_bound TO range_bound RBRACE
   33           | LBRACE range_bound TO range_bound RBRACKET

   34 range_bound: TERM
   35            | STAR


